content: Great emulator.. but it's not even original. After doing a tiny bit of digging, I found that this emulator is the EXACT same as Lemuroid. From what I heard, they made their code public and devs like these just steal it and make clones of the emulator.

Super good all in one emulator. There are some issues I've noticed. When loading saves in the DS emulator it will continously crash until I restart it, even then it doesn't keep every save and requires you to use save states. Haven't encountered it on the other emulators. Also adding cheats and GameShark codes would be nice ðŸ˜Š

Well worth the investment for an high quality all in one Emulators and plays well on my Samsung Galaxy S10E and ready to test this out on my Samsung Dex Station to try out some emulators to play some retro games
